Package game2048

package game2048
game2048 contains all necessary files and implementations to run a 2048 game instance.
  • Class
    Description
    Console2048
    The Console2048 class is a class that is used to see the actual GameModel2048 values.
    Game2048
    The Game2048 class holds the method for instantiating the game.
    GameController2048
    The GameController2048 class is a mediator between GameModel and GameGUI.
    GameGUI2048
    The GameGUI2048 class creates a window to represent the GameModel2048 class graphically.
    GameModel2048
    The GameModel2048 is the central component which directly manages the data, logic and rules of the game.
    GameModel2048.Direction
    These are the directions in which you can move the character
    GameModel2048.Events
    This is the events of the game, and they are used for keeping track of which event has occurred the game is in.
